        "This was the first time in tournament history that the top four teams in the FIFA Men's World Ranking (June 2026) all qualified for the World Cup semifinals",
        "Morocco, the only African team to reach the quarter-finals, were eliminated by France despite Mbappé missing an early penalty",
        "Half of the quarter-finals (Norway vs England and Argentina vs Switzerland) were decided in extra time, with none requiring a penalty shootout",
